= To Do List

The following is a list of planned expansions for HighLine, in no particular
order.

* Support <tt>ask(..., Array)</tt>, better than the current
  <tt>ask(..., lambda { |arr| arr.split(",") })</tt> or similar.
* Support <tt>ask(..., Hash)</tt>.
* Support <tt>ask(..., File)</tt>.
* Add readline support for history and editing.
* Add full column support to choose()
* Fix this bug:
      irb(main):015:0> HighLine.new.choose { |m|
      irb(main):016:1*   m.add("Anne-Marie") { "Anne-Marie" }
      irb(main):017:1>   m.add("Vincent") { "Vincent" }
      irb(main):018:1> }
      [1] Anne-Marie
      [2] Vincent
      ? 3
      You must enter a valid 12Anne-MarieVincent.
      ?  
